  - m_Id: 32
    m_Localized: Ready for action
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 33
    m_Localized: "Let\u2019s do this"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 34
    m_Localized: No fear!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35
    m_Localized: "Guys, I\u2019ll rescue you!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 36
    m_Localized: "You\u2019ll have to do better than that"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 37
    m_Localized: "It wasn\u2019t as hard as it looked"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38
    m_Localized: I still need more energy to activate it
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 39
    m_Localized: "I\u2019ve seen ugly people in my life, but this one takes the cake"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 40
    m_Localized: This place is full of horrible creatures!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41
    m_Localized: Who are you? And where are my companions?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 42
    m_Localized: "(Something the protagonist doesn\u2019t understand)"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 43
    m_Localized: Help! My village and your friends have been kidnapped
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 44
    m_Localized: "They\u2019re being forced to work extracting resources they want
      from this place"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45
    m_Localized: "I\u2019m not surprised, they do the same everywhere they go"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 46
    m_Localized: "I\u2019ll go look for them, I hope nothing serious has happened
      to them"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 47
    m_Localized: "Thank you very much, I\u2019ll show you where they took them"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 48
    m_Localized: Are you sure you want to quit?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 49
    m_Localized: Yes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 50
    m_Localized: No
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
